{"tid":1926594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【急急急】18區區議員, 要做野啦~~~~~~~~~~","createTime":"2020-03-15T08:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:41:26.000Z","uid":345002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bca20cb889853450f8b6c1e0e83d53b7141604","tid":1926594,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">今日差不多18區都有 23條街站, 叫人支持。突然咁張揚，背後一定有人支持。<br />\n我地區選大勝，唔係贏左就算架，人地吹緊２３條，９月選舉又快黎。<br />\n依家就係１８區區議員展示實力既時候啦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建議<br />\n1.叫人登記做選民 (日日街站, 依家學生唔使返學, 應該好多義工幫手)<br />\n2.向市民講解23條壞處 <br />\n3.向區內黃店講解點樣登記做公會 (功能組別) </span>[/size=6]<br />\n[size=5]<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n區選贏左, 依家係發揮作用既時候<br />\n屋企人如果未登記, 快D幫佢地登記啦。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">＊＊睇下對家幾落力，你會唔會有Ｄ驚？＊＊<br />\n＊＊我地要未雨綢繆啊，唔好學垃圾政府＊＊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">麻煩推到１８區都見到</div></span>"},{"pid":"1323de6c8e6fd8cdd2c33d1f111335b8ea09abdf","tid":1926594,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"麻煩推到１８區都見到"},{"pid":"89e30bcbe267728f7405a1428a03dbb2e53e8402","tid":1926594,"uid":137967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cefb406081483f470b6df29572bfdc5a9f911f","tid":1926594,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"麻煩推到１８區都見到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5dfe26e05e3b5ed090ebdc435c6421bc95b995","tid":1926594,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-